    "description": "'House of Rules' 是一款恐怖益智游戏，灵感来自于基于规则的creepypastas。 （被称为那不勒斯鬼故事）<br>遵循工作规则，解开各种谜题，揭开隐藏在豪宅中的真相。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Synopsis</strong></h2><br>在寻找工作地点时，您会发现一个有趣的招聘广告，提供过高的薪水。怀疑但绝望，你前往豪宅面试，发现令人惊讶的整洁工作场所，奇怪的工作规则和可疑的同事。你当场得到工作机会。你的工作明天开始。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><br>- Puzzles and riddles<br>- 20 Collectible endings<br>- Shocking twists<br>- Unique characters<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Parody and Streaming Guide</strong></h2><br>1. House of Rules strictly bans game unpacking and game modification.<br>2. Fan art, cartoons, and parodies are allowed as long as the source is indicated, non-commercial, and does not damage the original.<br>3. It is forbidden to upload videos with only the endings.<br>4. For endings 19 and 20, only live streaming is allowed.<br><br>In other cases, please send a mail to the developer.<br>(The guide may change in the full version.)",
